Ever since the beginning of our partnership with Eiichiro Oda, we have been working closely to bring the ONE PIECE live action to you. We share the same determination to invite everyone into the world of ONE PIECE.

in many ways, amy and danny occupy opposite sides of the spectrum in their lives, careers, and relationships.

but on a deeper level, they’re more alike than they realize: they’re both struggling with loneliness, disempowerment, and the pressure to live up to others’ expectations.

feeling out of control of their lives is what fuels their thrill-seeking behavior and their unwillingness to let their beef go; the conflict allows them to unleash their rage, frustration, and pain they can’t express anywhere else.

in a way, they need each other.
